This lab demonstrates basic log analysis using Splunk.

##  Splunk Query Used

index=_internal | top source

This query shows the most common log sources in the Splunk internal index.

## Findings

The logs show activity from the Splunk web interface.

Observations:

- Activity originates from localhost (127.0.0.1)
- The source log is `splunkd_ui_access.log`
- Events show HTTP GET requests to Splunk search endpoints

