## Security Insights

The analyzed logs show activity generated by the Splunk web interface.

Most of the events originate from the local machine (127.0.0.1), which indicates that the activity is coming from the system where Splunk is installed.

The source `splunkd_ui_access.log` records interactions with the Splunk web interface such as searches and requests to Splunk services.

